---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — Your Name"
  description="Learn about my background in UX design, my process, and the tools I use to create user-centered digital experiences."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16 sm:py-24">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 tracking-tight">
      About Me
    </h1>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        I'm a UX designer with a passion for making technology accessible
        and enjoyable for everyone. I believe great design is invisible —
        it just works.
      </p>
      <p>
        With a background in [your background], I bring a unique perspective
        to every project. I love the messy middle of the design process —
        synthesizing research, sketching ideas, and testing solutions with
        real users.
      </p>
      <p>
        When I'm not designing, you'll find me [your interests].
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        What I Do
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="p-5 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">UX Research</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
            User interviews, usability testing, surveys, and data analysis to uncover real needs.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Interaction Design</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
            Wireframes, prototypes, and flows that turn complex systems into intuitive experiences.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Visual Design</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
            Clean, modern interfaces with strong typography, color, and visual hierarchy.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Design Systems</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
            Scalable component libraries and design tokens for consistent product experiences.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 p-8 rounded-xl bg-gray-50 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Let's Work Together</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
        I'm always interested in new projects and collaborations.
      </p>
      <a
        href="mailto:hello@example.com"
        class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium rounded-lg bg-primary-600 text-white hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 focus-visible:ring-offset-2"
      >
        Say hello
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
